cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in academic work, please cite it as below."
title: "Sunrise CPD: Resource-Constrained Multi-Sensor Change-Point Detection on Sunrise Data"
abstract: >
  Empirical evaluation of a resource-constrained multi-sensor change-point
  detection framework on the SensorScope Grand-St-Bernard deployment, using
  astronomical sunrise as external ground truth and solar radiation as the
  observed signal.
authors:
  - family-names: "PRA"
    given-names: "Paulo Renato"
