date-released: "2026-05-07"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/paulorenatoaz/sunrise-cpd"
keywords:
  - change-point detection
  - CUSUM
  - multi-sensor
  - resource-constrained sensing
  - SensorScope
  - sunrise
